[
  {
    "id": "hint_layer_height",
    "text": "层高\n层高越小打印越精细，但耗时越长。常用范围: 0.1mm - 0.3mm。",
    "weight": 10,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Layer-height"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_infill",
    "text": "填充密度\n填充密度影响模型强度和重量。20% 适合大多数场景，100% 为实心。",
    "weight": 10,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Infill"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_support",
    "text": "支撑设置\n悬空角度超过 45° 的部分需要支撑。合理使用支撑可以提升打印质量。",
    "weight": 8,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Supports"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_speed",
    "text": "打印速度\n打印速度越快效率越高，但可能影响表面质量。建议先慢后快测试。",
    "weight": 7,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Speed"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_brims",
    "text": "Brim 裙边\nBrim（裙边）可以增加模型与热床的附着力，防止翘边。",
    "weight": 6,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Brim-for-better-adhesion"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_temperature",
    "text": "喷嘴温度\n喷嘴温度和热床温度需要根据耗材类型调整。PLA 通常 200°C/60°C。",
    "weight": 9,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Temperature"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_retract",
    "text": "回退设置\n回退设置可以减少空驶时的拉丝现象。调整回退距离和速度可改善表面质量。",
    "weight": 5,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Retraction"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_perimeters",
    "text": "壁层数\n外壁层数越多模型表面越光滑。通常 2-3 层即可获得良好效果。",
    "weight": 6,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Perimeters"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_adaptive_layer",
    "text": "自适应层高\n自适应层高根据模型表面角度自动调整层高，在平坦区域使用大层高提高速度，在细节区域使用小层高提升质量。",
    "weight": 4,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Adaptive-Layer-Height"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_multi_plate",
    "text": "多平板打印\n使用多平板功能可以将不同模型安排到不同平板上，方便批量打印。",
    "weight": 3,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Plates"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_gcode_preview",
    "text": "G-code 预览\n预览模式下可以逐层查看 G-code 路径，帮助您在打印前发现潜在问题。",
    "weight": 5,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Preview"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_variable_layer",
    "text": "可变层高\n可变层高功能可以在重要表面区域使用更小的层高，其余区域保持较大层高以节省时间。",
    "weight": 3,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Variable-Layer-Height"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_precise_wall",
    "text": "精确外壁\n开启精确外壁可以提升打印精度和层间一致性。",
    "weight": 5,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Precise-wall"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_sandwich_mode",
    "text": "三明治模式\n使用三明治模式（内-外-内）可以提升精度和层间一致性（适用于无明显悬垂的模型）。",
    "weight": 4,
    "documentation_link": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_chamber_temperature",
    "text": "腔体温度\nCrealityPrint 支持腔体温度设置，适用于 ABS/ASA 等需要封闭环境的耗材。",
    "weight": 4,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Chamber-temperature"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_calibration",
    "text": "打印机校准\n校准打印机可以显著提升打印质量。在 CrealityPrint 中可以使用内置校准解决方案。",
    "weight": 7,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Calibration"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_auxiliary_fan",
    "text": "辅助风扇\nCrealityPrint 支持辅助部件冷却风扇设置。",
    "weight": 3,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Auxiliary-fan"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_air_filtration",
    "text": "空气净化/排气风扇\nCrealityPrint 支持空气净化和排气风扇控制。",
    "weight": 3,
    "documentation_link": "https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer/wiki/Air-filtration"
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_keyboard_shortcuts",
    "text": "键盘快捷键\n按 <b>Tab</b> 键可以在准备和预览工作区之间快速切换。按 <b>C</b> 键可以开关 G-code 窗口。",
    "weight": 4,
    "documentation_link": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_reverse_on_odd",
    "text": "奇数层反转\n<b>奇数层反转</b>功能可以显著改善悬垂部分的表面质量。",
    "weight": 3,
    "documentation_link": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_cut_tool",
    "text": "切割工具\n您可以使用切割工具在任意角度和位置切割模型。",
    "weight": 4,
    "documentation_link": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "hint_auto_arrange",
